    "rationale": "All 7 assessed credibility factors meet or exceed MRL 2 required levels. The CFD model demonstrates sufficient fidelity to identify worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump under CPB conditions. The relative hemolysis index criterion (RH < 1) is supported by experimental validation with 8.4% mean error and conservative over-prediction bias. The credibility assessment supports regulatory submission for the Class II CPB device.",
